Text:
Finnish subtitles are mostly swedish and rest of them are translated by google. Here's example:

"Englannissa vihaaja vuoden 1215 koskeneet
Audiovisuaalinen King John 16 vuotta.
Kuten julma audiovisuaalisen Englanti
Kings"

The same with the Norwegian sub. Custom swedesh-google-translated. Poor quality.

Video itself was good though.

Next time, wait for retails Darklord2011.
